{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f0ecd0f221","title":"江青看《杜泉山》剧后的讲话","origin":"文化部办公厅提供","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"669a6b0295","index":0,"year":1973,"month":6,"day":25,"articleId":"f0ecd0f221"}],"tags":[{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"213d6826d5","type":"title","text":"江青看《杜泉山》剧后的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f0ecd0f221"},{"id":"da81515634","type":"authors","text":"江青","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f0ecd0f221"},{"id":"a725c64ac7","type":"paragraph","text":"一九七三年六月二十五日夜至二十六日凌晨","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f0ecd0f221"},{"id":"6c8b4f07ee","type":"paragraph","text":"《杜》、《平》要赶快改出来，“七·一”“八·一”分别发表，“七·一”来不及可不演出。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f0ecd0f221"},{"id":"83200c9e23","type":"paragraph","text":"《杜》剧布景，杜鹃花不红，可以去湖南看看。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f0ecd0f221"},{"id":"87ec3a742b","type":"paragraph","text":"闪电老是在一个地方，一个样子。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f0ecd0f221"},{"id":"622e9c4e2a","type":"paragraph","text":"柯湘的衣服，要改为暖色的。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f0ecd0f221"},{"id":"e5eed4dfed","type":"paragraph","text":"(姚文元：唱词改改，太文了。)","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f0ecd0f221"},{"id":"d96edf65c6","type":"paragraph","text":"艺校搞点小孩舞蹈，红绸舞、剑舞、青蛙舞、京剧的对舞。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f0ecd0f221"},{"id":"1ecd1bf106","type":"paragraph","text":"筝不叫古筝，就叫筝。许多乐器都是古代传下来的。把人调到中央乐团去。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f0ecd0f221"},{"id":"705ab138c6","type":"paragraph","text":"剑舞还是用《夜深沉》曲牌。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f0ecd0f221"},{"id":"7a13582548","type":"paragraph","text":"舞蹈通知总政，除了红海洋外，还要搞帮助民兵训练，要有男民兵、女民兵，体现军民联防，要有个女民兵连长。可以长一些。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f0ecd0f221"},{"id":"ca51b30aaf","type":"paragraph","text":"我们抓中小型抓晚了。要集中力量抓一下小歌、小舞、小戏，人们说我们贪大求全。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f0ecd0f221"},{"id":"2cc0e19604","type":"paragraph","text":"北京京剧团《草原烽火》要离开原作，原作者很坏，奴隶写成奴才。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f0ecd0f221"},{"id":"fcfa691253","type":"paragraph","text":"《白毛女》我没有说过让大春、喜儿相会，不要离开阶级斗争。大春也不要一个人去参军，可带几个人。也不一定在根据地，可以打游击。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f0ecd0f221"},{"id":"cc20056eec","type":"paragraph","text":"有人说杨白劳改得反抗太多了，杨白劳反抗要有，但不要过分。原来喜儿哭爹一场很动人，现在比较平。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f0ecd0f221"},{"id":"f350b2b12b","type":"paragraph","text":"一台音乐舞蹈节目很精彩，但化妆太难看，眉毛短，眼睛象个窟窿。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f0ecd0f221"},{"id":"5982f258eb","type":"paragraph","text":"署名，《平原》好办，《杜》大部分是于会泳搞的，都有王××参加，署王××等集体创作吧。还要搞个话剧。","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f0ecd0f221"},{"id":"8e2421d455","type":"paragraph","text":"柯湘主调音乐要京剧化一点。现在我跟你们说，京剧还是要姓京。","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f0ecd0f221"},{"id":"249359f28a","type":"appellation","text":"(文化部办公厅提供)","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f0ecd0f221"}],"page":{"id":"4a5dbe56d3","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f0ecd0f221","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}